00038 void testParamContainer()
00039 {
00040     if (os_) *os_ << "testParamContainer()\n"; 
00041 
00042     ParamContainer pc;
00043     pc.paramGroupPtrs.push_back(ParamGroupPtr(new ParamGroup("pg1")));
00044     pc.paramGroupPtrs.push_back(ParamGroupPtr(new ParamGroup("pg2")));
00045 
00046     MSData msd;
00047     msd.paramGroupPtrs.push_back(ParamGroupPtr(new ParamGroup("pg2")));
00048     msd.paramGroupPtrs.push_back(ParamGroupPtr(new ParamGroup("pg1")));
00049     msd.paramGroupPtrs[0]->cvParams.push_back(MS_reflectron_on);
00050     msd.paramGroupPtrs[1]->cvParams.push_back(MS_reflectron_off);
00051 
00052     unit_assert(pc.paramGroupPtrs[0]->cvParams.empty());
00053     unit_assert(pc.paramGroupPtrs[1]->cvParams.empty());
00054 
00055     References::resolve(pc, msd);
00056 
00057     unit_assert(pc.paramGroupPtrs[0]->cvParams.size() == 1);
00058     unit_assert(pc.paramGroupPtrs[0]->cvParams[0] == MS_reflectron_off);
00059     unit_assert(pc.paramGroupPtrs[1]->cvParams.size() == 1);
00060     unit_assert(pc.paramGroupPtrs[1]->cvParams[0] == MS_reflectron_on);
